This is (or will be) a FUSE filesystem capable of using Spotify for
streaming music.
Currently its in a pre-alpha proof of concept stage.

Usage:

1. Mount the filesystem

2. Use

Filesystem structure:

Playlists/
Starred/
Search/


More to come 

